        <abstract><p>Rajashri Pandit <persName ref="#gangadhar">Gangadharji</persName>, tax-proceeds holder (mokasadar) of <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, confirms that the assessed taxes for 3 villages for the autumn and spring harvest of Fasli year 1150 have been received in accordance with the official assessment and the contract with headman (muqaddam) <persName ref="#babuKhan">Babu Khan</persName>, son of Fazil Khan. </p></abstract>       
